      <title>Hello Word</title>
      <link href="/hello-word/"/>
      <url>/hello-word/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基本框架"><a href="#基本框架" class="headerlink" title="基本框架"></a>基本框架</h1><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span>  <span class="comment">//主函数-程序的入口-有且仅有一个</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>int 是整形的意思</strong><br><strong>main前面的int表示函数调用返回一个整型值</strong><br><strong>return 0；返回0  （前后呼应）</strong></p><h1 id="数据类型"><a href="#数据类型" class="headerlink" title="数据类型"></a>数据类型</h1><p>char &#x2F;&#x2F;字符数据型<br>short &#x2F;&#x2F;短整型<br>int &#x2F;&#x2F;整型<br>long &#x2F;&#x2F;长整型<br>long long &#x2F;&#x2F;更长的整型<br>float &#x2F;&#x2F;单精度浮点型<br>double &#x2F;&#x2F;双精度浮点型</p><h2 id="各种类型大小"><a href="#各种类型大小" class="headerlink" title="各种类型大小"></a>各种类型大小</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">char</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">short</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">int</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">long</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">long</span> <span class="type">long</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">float</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%zd\n&quot;</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">double</span>));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="关于打印"><a href="#关于打印" class="headerlink" title="关于打印"></a>关于打印</h1><p>printf(“文本”)   打印文本  \n换行符<br>%c  打印字符格式的数据<br>%d  打印整型十进制的数据<br>%f   打印浮点型<br>%p  打印地址形式</p><h1 id="字节"><a href="#字节" class="headerlink" title="字节"></a>字节</h1><p>计算机中的单位<br>bit——比特位<br>byte-字节<br><strong>1byte&#x3D;8bit</strong></p><h1 id="变量"><a href="#变量" class="headerlink" title="变量"></a>变量</h1><p>变量包括局部变量和全局变量<br>main内称为局部变量<br>main外称为全局变量<br>全局变量适用于整个项目<br>{}称为代码块<br>局部变量和全局变量尽量不要相同，当相同时，局部变量优先被选择</p><h1 id="作用域"><a href="#作用域" class="headerlink" title="作用域"></a>作用域</h1><p>变量哪里可以用哪里就是作用域<br>extern 声明外部符号</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
